# Of or pertaining to the [[culture]], people, or products of [[South Asia]].

====Usage notes====
* For South Asians abroad, it has become a term that mainly identifies other fellow South Asians.
* '''Desi''' is often used in lieu of Indian as it allows for inclusion of non-Indian South Asian groups who have since been separated from India after Partition i.e. Pakistan and Bangladesh
*: ''e.g.'': '''Desi''' food refers to South Asian food like rice, dal, chapatti etc.
* '''Desi''' dance can refer to the popular dances in the movies to Punjabi dance, ''[[bhangra]]'' to classical dances like Bharathnatya, Kuchipudi etc.

